'''硒酸铈(III)'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Ce<sub>2</sub>(SeO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。它可由[[硒酸|硒酸]]和[[碳酸铈|碳酸铈]]反应得到，蒸发溶剂析出晶体。<ref>Perkovskaya, Yu. B.; Sukhanova, I. M. Rare earth metal selenates. ''Metody Polucheniya Khimicheskikh Reaktivov i Preparatov'', 1967. 16: 120-123. ISSN: 0539-5143.</ref>将硒酸铈和[[硒酸铯|硒酸铯]]在水溶液中混合，蒸发结晶，可得到复盐CsCe(SeO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>·4H<sub>2</sub>O。<ref>Ovanesyan, S. M.; Iskhakova, L. D.; Trunov, V. K. Preparation and crystal structure of cesium rare earth selenate tetrahydrates (CsTR(SeO4)​2·4H2O). ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 1987. 32 (4): 896-900. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>

